{"tid":1517257,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被指調味包包裝辱警 翠華澄清：沒有任何影射意味","createTime":"2019-08-30T01:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T01:23:13.000Z","uid":56881,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"89f8e78b2afb32d7191fc664314f77b9ff66f6be","tid":1517257,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:19:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%AA%BF%E5%91%B3%E5%8C%85%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%9D%E8%BE%B1%E8%AD%A6-%E7%BF%A0%E8%8F%AF%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%BD%B1%E5%B0%84%E6%84%8F%E5%91%B3-124100495.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%2591%25B3%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%258C%2585%25E8%25A3%259D%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%25BF%25A0%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25BE%2584%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%2591%25B3-124100495.html&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8lTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=25081736\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%AA%BF%E5%91%B3%E5%8C%85%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%9D%E8%BE%B1%E8%AD%A6-%E7%BF%A0%E8%8F%AF%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%BD%B1%E5%B0%84%E6%84%8F%E5%91%B3-124100495.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7b078R.6jpaCdXdB.P8L9w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190829a204348.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7b078R.6jpaCdXdB.P8L9w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190829a204348.jpg&h=5b6607d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上流傳翠華餐廳最新的調味包包裝有諷刺警察之嫌，引發網民關注。網圖<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】修訂《逃犯條例》事件波及餐飲業，網上流傳連鎖集團翠華餐廳最新的調味包包裝有諷刺警察之嫌，引發大批網民關注，更有人揚言要罷食翠華。翠華集團澄清，調味包包裝設計早於2015年設計，亦沒有任何影射意味，指會對失實流傳，或別有用心破壞集團聲譽等行為，保留法律追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n港區全國人大代表吳秋北今日在facebook上載了一張翠華餐廳各種調味包的照片，當中包括印有穿著制服的動物的胡椒及白糖包裝，並配以「出椒」、「下一代，睇我哋」等字句。吳秋北斥責翠華餐廳這些產品包裝疑似辱警，稱該疑似是「狗頭」的圖案是「缺乏正義感的幽默」，更稱如出於仇警，「必將自食其果！」<br />\n<br />\n另外，前新聞統籌專員馮煒光亦指，翠華的調味包包裝設計是「暗合黑衣示威者對警察」，例如「比喻警察為狗」，是呼應反修例運動示威者的口號。<br />\n<br />\n翠華集團其後更發表聲明澄清，指早於2015年，集團已做了品牌重塑計劃，當中包括特別設計了一系列「奶油豬卡通圖案」。而包裝紙上的標語「下一代睇我哋 Use it! Recycle it!」原意是在源頭著手呼籲客人響應環保。翠華集團重申，所有設計並沒有任何影射意味，「並會就網上失實的流傳及刻意抹黑，或別有用心破壞集團聲譽等行為，保留法律追究權利」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來翠華都係自己人<br />\n多謝翠華！<br />\n翠華好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2d7b4acaefa8d69f0e6a95cff83780d5acc2ed","tid":1517257,"uid":13115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:21:27.000Z","msg":"對號入座<br />\n嬲嬲豬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4c355c1286e0a6c1aedea886a8232a984c597c","tid":1517257,"uid":26976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:22:04.000Z","msg":"2015年味雨革之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來翠華一直默默咁支持緊<br />\n全靠佢運動先可以死灰復燃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e976bb67e4d4903c2b26eb0e86254d697ae18676","tid":1517257,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:23:13.000Z","msg":"支持翠華法律追究吳秋北同馮煒光<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}